Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:26.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:31.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:37.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:37.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:45.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:45.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:47.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:53.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:53.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:58.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:00:58.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:04.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:09.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:11.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:15.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:15.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:20.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:26.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:26.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:31.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:31.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:36.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:36.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:42.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:42.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:47.37,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:47.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:55.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:57.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.09,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:01.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:06.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:06.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:11.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:11.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:17.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:17.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:25.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy made it to Marineford to rescue \Nhis brother, Ace who will be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He and the Whitebeards have invaded to \Nthe plaza to make it to the scaffold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the midst of the Navy's onslaught, \Nwith the Whitebeards' assistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy ran on the path that Inazuma \Ncreated and finally made it to Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a remnant from the old times!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no ship that can \Nbear me in the new era!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get it over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Power That Can Burn Even \NFire! Akainu's Ruthless Pursuit!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Marineford is in danger!\N--Stop Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:27.56,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ABSOLUTE JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's willing to destroy the whole island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna leave you! \NYou gotta come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you disobey your Captain's order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just go, fools?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:05:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is our chance! Kill \NWhitebeard! He's dying already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Let's do as Pops said!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind leaving Pops behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, how dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! No one wants to leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grumbling about it at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like this is the same as trampling \Non Pops' determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get ready to sail out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna leave soon! Come on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Marco, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You messed with us!\N--Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! All I want is to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wax is as strong as steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that a \Nnormal sword can cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also a Devil Fruit eater!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong enough to try to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N"Fire Fist" even at Fleet Admiral Sengoku's elbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, don't overestimate me \Nlike that! I'm not a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he still has that much \Npower after getting wounded so badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he isn't concerned about \N"Fire Fist" Ace anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleet Admiral Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear his intention is to \Nsink Marineford into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to change the era? \NYeah, the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His allies who have been \Nsold out are all dead now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the connection still out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long should we wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We couldn't see the whole picture
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbecause Buggy the Clown stood in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy over there must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great pirate--Captain Buggy the Clown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's who I am indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he want to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done, I can't report \Nanything to the head office!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on at Marineford now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Transponder Snail hasn't come out yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Captain Buggy is about to beat \NWhitebeard - it's no time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it as if it's so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dying but he still has boundless \Npower - didn't they see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I even say that I'm gonna beat \Nthat man?! I really screwed this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it! It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We gotta broadcast Captain \NBuggy's big moment all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it out at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Come out now!\N--Or we're gonna burn you out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we gotta soak it into water!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's do that!\N--Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop it, fools!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he volunteered \Nto be a slave for the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he got beaten up in the \Nbattlefield like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel sorry for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let him go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we gotta cancel "Captain \NBuggy's beating beard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and broadcast it live to the world" plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Even you want to \Npull out from Marineford?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you, Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes down to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're all strong guys who've \Nbeen locked up in Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better not make enemies of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Transponder Snail came out voluntarily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! He came out because he was \Ntouched by Captain Buggy's kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy can even win \Nthe hearts of the Snails!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's amazing as we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the man who will conquer \Nthe world - he's our Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn bastard! Why didn't \Nhe just stay inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's no way that I can back out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy, make a declaration \Nto conquer the world now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's your moment!\N--Smoke: good, lighting: good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I mean... Dammit! \NThis leaves me one choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, shoot my bravery!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture the moment that I kill Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, look!\N--The picture's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't see what's going \Non because of the smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Navy losing?! What \Nhappened to Whitebeard and Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Um, well...\N--Transponder Snail, go lower!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everyone! I'm Buggy and I'm a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the sea now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We who remain have to go back \Nto the New World safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away! \NKill as many as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one that you \Nought to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Jozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's badly \Ninjured but he'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain gave us an order! Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brenheim! You gotta carry Jozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw boy! Why are you standing around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, let's go! The old man \Nhas made up his mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! And it won't be in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back off, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need words now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy to have me as your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still some fight left in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are too valuable to let die now, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still wanna run wild, run as wild \Nas you want on the sea under my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The scaffold was destroyed!\N--So was the Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Ace get executed?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move the camera to Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Buggy and I'm a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great pirate--Captain Buggy the Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you're \Ngonna beat Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with his head in your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're willing to become \None of The Four Emperors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Buggy and I'm a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just repeating that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something forward-looking! \NLet's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with Buggy! Show us \NMarineford as it stands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not what we're interested in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean... I just wanna \Ndo something flashy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Run to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ace-san, Luffy-kun, get in front of me!\N--Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to get you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what the good old man wants \Nis as many survivors as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've stolen a Navy ship! Get on board quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they really think that they can \Nget away?! How simple they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral Sakazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, move aside a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, just keep going \Nuntil you get to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you rescue \N"Fire Fist" Ace, you run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Whitebeards must be a group of cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to stir you up obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stop, you're playing into his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well your captain is that guy \Nso you can't help it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because after all, Whitebeard is just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...loser from the old times!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:17:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take back what you just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't, Ace! Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let him say whatever he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He mocked Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say "take it back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in a million years! I'll tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father Gold Roger \Nconquered the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and opened the door to the new era called
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe Great Pirate Era by sacrificing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Navy admiral, it's \Nnot my place to say so,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was true to his name: \Nthe King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In contrast, what has Whitebeard done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he really had \Nthe intention to fight .
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:18:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that he established \Na large family someplace
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was satisfied being a \Nbig fish in a little barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some fools in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who'd say that his name is \Nkeeping peace on various islands
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you ask me, he's just keeping \Nlightweights in fear of him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he thinks that he's a \Nhero which makes me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Roger was alive, \NWhitebeard had second billing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even after Roger's death, \Nhe couldn't become a King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means he'll never better Roger \Nand he'll be a loser forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who Whitebeard \Nis and that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a poor man when you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHe gathered some punks who call him Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and roamed around the sea \Nwith his fake family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And although he reigned the sea for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he couldn't become a King and gained nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and at the end, he was stabbed by a fool,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\None of his sons who fell for my line
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he will die to protect that son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that his life is so empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Ace, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops gave us a place to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't understand his greatness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People don't deserve to live \Nif they can't live justly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punks like you guys don't \Ndeserve a place to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard will die as a loser! It's \Nfitting for a big fish in a little barrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard is a great pirate \Nwho shaped this era!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of the man who saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this era should be "Whitebeard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Whitebeard and you \Nguys who call him Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the same after all--losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace has been burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you careless because you \Nate a Logia type fruit which
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the most powerful of all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just fire but my \Nmagma can even burn fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My power is far stronger than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy-kun, you should not fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace's Vivre Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger the King of the Pirates, \NDragon--the revolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was amazed to hear that sons \Nof those two are step brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two have bad blood in your veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if the others get \Naway as long as I get you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is certainly a Vivre Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't told you that this card
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also tells you how much \Nvital energy the owner has.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card belongs to someone \Nwho you care for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.93,0:22:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's my brother's!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.82,0:22:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold onto it, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That paper will lead us to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is pierced by Akainu's \Nfist while protecting Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei and the Whitebeard \NPirates try to save him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Ace, realizing he is about to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,finds the voice to convey his feelings \Nto his friends one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Looking for the Answer! Fire Fist Ace \NDies on the Battlefield!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
